    "name": "Astoria Current",
    "detail": "Really a good deal for your money with daily breakfast included, even better than the breakfast buffets we had on numerous occasions in Hawaii. Everything at the hotel is in excellent shape. My son loves the beach in front of the hotel and also the hotel’s swimming pool. The staff is so nice and extremely helpful, especially Ferdy the food and drinks manager and Rene the restaurant staff. When my son needs milk before he sleeps Ferry makes sure it’s delivered to our room every night and the staff even washed his milk bottle for us a couple times because we forgot the bottle brush. They totally went out of their way to make us feel so welcome and have an enjoyable stay. Our first time to the Philippines and Boracay, didn’t know what to expect but now I’m really glad we picked it the Astoria Current. Would definitely come back again in the future!",
