    "detail": "Our flight from Manila via Air Phil was delayed by more than 4 hours. So, it was already past 5:00p.m. and have to be diverted to Kalibo airport. Travel another 1-1/2 hr. by land to Caticlan jetty port. We arrived the resort almost 9;00p.m. But, the staffs were at the lobby welcoming us with cold towels and welcome drinks. The check-in procedure was swift and we were guided to our room. Our rooms were huge- it's the right word to describe it. The resort was located in boat station 1 which is the best part of Boracay island. Definitely enjoyed my stay in this hotel and will be back soon.",
